'''Sébastien Kamba''' (wavutse ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1941), niUmukinnyi wa firime [[Kongo|muri  Kongo]]<ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/s%C3%A9bastien-kamba</ref> .  Umwe mu bakora amafilime yambere mu nganda za firime zo muri [[congo]], yayoboye filime ngufi ku bufatanye n’abakora amafilime y’Abafaransa<ref>https://peoplepill.com/people/sebastien-kamba</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Ukuboza 1941 i Brazzaville, muri [[Kongo|Repubulika ya Kongo]]<ref>https://ifcinema.institutfrancais.com/en/search?q_text=S%C3%A9bastien%20Kamba</ref> .

== Umwuga ==
Yimukiye mu [[Bufaransa]], yiga mu biro bishinzwe ubufatanye bwa Radiofonique<ref>https://www.editions-harmattan.fr/livre-production_cinematographique_et_parti_unique_l_exemple_du_congo_sebastien_kamba-9782738412584-2558.html</ref> . Nyuma yaje kwimenyereza umwuga kuri tereviziyo i Paris ndetse anaba umwarimu<ref>http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-no92026173</ref>.  Mu 1964, Kamba yakoze filime yambere yimpimbano ya [[Congo Brazzaville|congo]], film ngufi ya politiki ''Le Peuple du Congo-Léo vaincra'' <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/sebastien-kamba</ref>. Yakozwe ku bufatanye n’itangazamakuru rya tereviziyo.<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/sebastien-kamba/credits/3030431460/</ref>

Mu 1966, yakoze ''Kaka yo nayo ngufi'' hanyuma ''Mwana keba''  muri 1970.<ref>https://www.torinofilmfest.org/en/16-torino-film-festival/film/kaka-yo---rien-que-toi/1311/</ref>  Mu 1973, Kamba yayoboye filime ya mbere yagaragaye muri Repubulika ya [[Kongo]]: ''Al Rançon d'une alliance''<ref>https://www.decitre.fr/auteur/418922/Sebastien+Kamba</ref>, yakuwe mu gitabo cyitwa 'La légende de Mfoumou Ma Mazono' cyanditswe na Jean Malonga.<ref>https://www.centreculturelzola.com/comit%C3%A9-artistique/sebastien-kamba</ref>  Mu 1992, yasohoye igitabo ''Cinématographique et Parti Unique'' (Cinematographic Production and Unique Party. Urugero rwa Kongo).<ref>https://mediatheques-congo.org/index.php?lvl=author_see&id=8021</ref> 

Ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2019, i Brazzaville habereye igikombe cya mbere cy’ibikombe bya sinema muri [[Congo]] cyiswe "Les Kamba's Awards" mu rwego rwo guha icyubahiro Kamba.<ref>https://mediatheques-niger.org/index.php?lvl=author_see&id=80931</ref> 

